title: 'Lshaped Lounge'
body: Good One Improvement Points: A. The density of the foam used must be specified, we don't know what is there inside B. As the set contains two disjoint pieces, can think of providing joiners, so that they don't move freely C. The packing requires improvement, especially corners as handling damages could be noticed D. Back cushions are good but the outer cover can't be removed, for washing purposes. E. If an upper covering cloth for the whole of the L-shaped lounge can be designed, that would be nice, as this is non-washable, the only way is to dry clean by a vacuum cleaner!!  It is less than two months since we have been using it, it has a warranty for three years, let us see how the usage journey takes the shape
